window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Something vital is missing from David Hero's comfortable, ordinary existence. One day is much like the next, simple, predictable...boring. </p> <p>But the nights! Each night David Hero finds himself transported to a marvelous world where brave men and women battle terrible creatures possessed of cruel, dark powers. </p> <p>Despite his fears, the Dreamworlds tempt David, drawing him farther and farther from the waking world. Here he finds noble warriors; beautiful, loving women; and challenges almost greater than he can imagine. </p>"; 
